Task Manager v2.0
A powerful and user-friendly command-line task manager written in Python. Manage your daily tasks with categories, tags, priorities, and status tracking.

Features
Add, edit, and delete tasks

Organize tasks by categories and tags

Mark tasks as complete or incomplete

View tasks filtered by status, category, or tag

Search tasks by keywords

Task priority management: High, Medium, Low

View task statistics

Command-line interface with clear menu navigation

